flowchart LR
    OS[Off-chain Source 1<br/>Coinbase] --> AGG[Chainlink Aggregator<br/>median + heartbeat]
    OS2[Off-chain Source 2<br/>Binance] --> AGG
    OS3[Off-chain Source N] --> AGG
